node.text: Six years ago, Tony Hawk found a viral video of a 7-year-old girl landing a heel flip in a princess costume. Today, Rayssa Leal (13 years old) wins a silver medal at the Olympics with Tony Hawk as her mentor. Amazing story 🇧🇷
